Sentencas: For an extremely efficient power generation using biomass, a renewable energy, we investigated characteristics of an autothermal downdraft gasifier and SOFCs.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass

Sentencas: Cypress chips were converted into gasified gases with the efficiency of 90%.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass

Sentencas: The gasification rate saturated as the air flow rate increased, because of the heat losses from char surfaces via radiation and convection.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass

Sentencas: For the discharge of SOFCs, electrochemical H-2 oxidation was more dominant than CO oxidation in a model gasified gas, due to water gas shift reaction and selective electrochemical H-2 oxidation via H-spillover.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass

Sentencas: Electrochemical H2O reduction was inhibited by strongly adsorbed CO on Ni in the model gasified gas with the reverse bias operation.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass

Sentencas: The maximum polarization resistances of an anode-supported cell were more than two times larger than the charge transfer resistances in the model gasified gas.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass

Sentencas: The power density in the model gasified gas attained 62% of that in humidified H-2 at 0.8 V.
Titulo: Characteristics of solid oxide fuel cells in gasified gases from biomass
